17#define RRTYPE_TSIG_ATTRIBUTES \
18 (DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_META | DNS_RDATATYPEATTR_NOTQUESTION)

20static inline isc_result_t
21fromtext_any_tsig(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
22 isc_token_t token;
23 dns_name_t name;
24 uint64_t sigtime;
25 isc_buffer_t buffer;
26 dns_rcode_t rcode;
27 long i;
28 char *e;
29
30 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
31 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
32
33 UNUSED(type);
34 UNUSED(rdclass);
35 UNUSED(callbacks);
36
37 /*
38 * Algorithm Name.
39 */
40 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
41 false));
42 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
43 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
44 if (origin == NULL)
45 origin = dns_rootname;
46 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
47
48 /*
49 * Time Signed: 48 bits.
50 */
51 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
52 false));
53 sigtime = strtoull(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
54 if (*e != 0)
55 RETTOK(DNS_R_SYNTAX);
56 if ((sigtime >> 48) != 0)
57 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
58 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer((uint16_t)(sigtime >> 32), target));
59 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer((uint32_t)(sigtime & 0xffffffffU), target));
60
61 /*
62 * Fudge.
63 */
64 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
65 false));
66 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
67 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
68 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
69
70 /*
71 * Signature Size.
72 */
73 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
74 false));
75 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
76 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
77 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
78
79 /*
80 * Signature.
81 */
82 RETERR(isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, (int)token.value.as_ulong));
83
84 /*
85 * Original ID.
86 */
87 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
88 false));
89 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
90 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
91 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
92
93 /*
94 * Error.
95 */
96 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
97 false));
98 if (dns_tsigrcode_fromtext(&rcode, &token.value.as_textregion)
99 != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
100 {
101 i = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
102 if (*e != 0)
103 RETTOK(DNS_R_UNKNOWN);
104 if (i < 0 || i > 0xffff)
105 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
106 rcode = (dns_rcode_t)i;
107 }
108 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(rcode, target));
109
110 /*
111 * Other Len.
112 */
113 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
114 false));
115 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffffU)
116 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
117 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
118
119 /*
120 * Other Data.
121 */
122 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, (int)token.value.as_ulong));
123}

125static inline isc_result_t
126totext_any_tsig(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
127 isc_region_t sr;
128 isc_region_t sigr;
129 char buf[sizeof(" 281474976710655 ")];
130 char *bufp;
131 dns_name_t name;
132 dns_name_t prefix;
133 bool sub;
134 uint64_t sigtime;
135 unsigned short n;
136
137 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
138 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
139 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
140
141 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
142 /*
143 * Algorithm Name.
144 */
145 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
146 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
147 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
148 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
149 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
150 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
151 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
152
153 /*
154 * Time Signed.
155 */
156 sigtime = ((uint64_t)sr.base[0] << 40) |
157 ((uint64_t)sr.base[1] << 32) |
158 ((uint64_t)sr.base[2] << 24) |
159 ((uint64_t)sr.base[3] << 16) |
160 ((uint64_t)sr.base[4] << 8) |
161 (uint64_t)sr.base[5];
162 isc_region_consume(&sr, 6);
163 bufp = &buf[sizeof(buf) - 1];
164 *bufp-- = 0;
165 *bufp-- = ' ';
166 do {
167 *bufp-- = decdigits[sigtime % 10];
168 sigtime /= 10;
169 } while (sigtime != 0);
170 bufp++;
171 RETERR(str_totext(bufp, target));
172
173 /*
174 * Fudge.
175 */
176 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
177 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
178 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", n);
179 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
180
181 /*
182 * Signature Size.
183 */
184 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
185 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
186 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", n);
187 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
188
189 /*
190 * Signature.
191 */
192 if (n != 0U) {
193 REQUIRE(n <= sr.length);
194 sigr = sr;
195 sigr.length = n;
196 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
197 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
198 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
199 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
200 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sigr, 60, "", target));
201 else
202 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sigr, tctx->width - 2,
203 tctx->linebreak, target));
204 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
205 RETERR(str_totext(" ) ", target));
206 else
207 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
208 isc_region_consume(&sr, n);
209 } else {
210 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
211 }
212
213 /*
214 * Original ID.
215 */
216 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
217 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
218 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", n);
219 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
220
221 /*
222 * Error.
223 */
224 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
225 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
226 RETERR(dns_tsigrcode_totext((dns_rcode_t)n, target));
227
228 /*
229 * Other Size.
230 */
231 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
232 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
233 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), " %u ", n);
234 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
235
236 /*
237 * Other.
238 */
239 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
240 return (isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
241 else
242 return (isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, " ", target));
243}

245static inline isc_result_t
246fromwire_any_tsig(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
247 isc_region_t sr;
248 dns_name_t name;
249 unsigned long n;
250
251 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
252 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
253
254 UNUSED(type);
255 UNUSED(rdclass);
256
257 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
258
259 /*
260 * Algorithm Name.
261 */
262 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
263 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
264
265 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
266 /*
267 * Time Signed + Fudge.
268 */
269 if (sr.length < 8)
270 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
271 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 8));
272 isc_region_consume(&sr, 8);
273 isc_buffer_forward(source, 8);
274
275 /*
276 * Signature Length + Signature.
277 */
278 if (sr.length < 2)
279 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
280 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
281 if (sr.length < n + 2)
282 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
283 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, n + 2));
284 isc_region_consume(&sr, n + 2);
285 isc_buffer_forward(source, n + 2);
286
287 /*
288 * Original ID + Error.
289 */
290 if (sr.length < 4)
291 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
292 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 4));
293 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
294 isc_buffer_forward(source, 4);
295
296 /*
297 * Other Length + Other.
298 */
299 if (sr.length < 2)
300 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
301 n = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
302 if (sr.length < n + 2)
303 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
304 isc_buffer_forward(source, n + 2);
305 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, n + 2));
306}

308static inline isc_result_t
309towire_any_tsig(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
310 isc_region_t sr;
311 dns_name_t name;
312 dns_offsets_t offsets;
313
314 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
315 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
316 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
317
318 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
319 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
320 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
321 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
322 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
323 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
324 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
325}

327static inline int
328compare_any_tsig(ARGS_COMPARE) {
329 isc_region_t r1;
330 isc_region_t r2;
331 dns_name_t name1;
332 dns_name_t name2;
333 int order;
334
335 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
336 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
337 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
338 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
339 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
340 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
341
342 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
343 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
344 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
345 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
346 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &r1);
347 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &r2);
348 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
349 if (order != 0)
350 return (order);
351 isc_region_consume(&r1, name_length(&name1));
352 isc_region_consume(&r2, name_length(&name2));
353 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
354}

356static inline isc_result_t
357fromstruct_any_tsig(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
358 dns_rdata_any_tsig_t *tsig = source;
359 isc_region_t tr;
360
361 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
362 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
363 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
364 REQUIRE(tsig->common.rdclass == rdclass);
365 REQUIRE(tsig->common.rdtype == type);
366
367 UNUSED(type);
368 UNUSED(rdclass);
369
370 /*
371 * Algorithm Name.
372 */
373 RETERR(name_tobuffer(&tsig->algorithm, target));
374
375 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tr);
376 if (tr.length < 6 + 2 + 2)
377 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
378
379 /*
380 * Time Signed: 48 bits.
381 */
382 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer((uint16_t)(tsig->timesigned >> 32),
383 target));
384 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer((uint32_t)(tsig->timesigned & 0xffffffffU),
385 target));
386
387 /*
388 * Fudge.
389 */
390 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tsig->fudge, target));
391
392 /*
393 * Signature Size.
394 */
395 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tsig->siglen, target));
396
397 /*
398 * Signature.
399 */
400 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, tsig->signature, tsig->siglen));
401
402 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tr);
403 if (tr.length < 2 + 2 + 2)
404 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
405
406 /*
407 * Original ID.
408 */
409 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tsig->originalid, target));
410
411 /*
412 * Error.
413 */
414 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tsig->error, target));
415
416 /*
417 * Other Len.
418 */
419 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(tsig->otherlen, target));
420
421 /*
422 * Other Data.
423 */
424 return (mem_tobuffer(target, tsig->other, tsig->otherlen));
425}

427static inline isc_result_t
428tostruct_any_tsig(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
429 dns_rdata_any_tsig_t *tsig;
430 dns_name_t alg;
431 isc_region_t sr;
432
433 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
434 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
435 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
436
437 tsig = (dns_rdata_any_tsig_t *) target;
438 tsig->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
439 tsig->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
440 ISC_LINK_INIT(&tsig->common, link);
441
442 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
443
444 /*
445 * Algorithm Name.
446 */
447 dns_name_init(&alg, NULL);
448 dns_name_fromregion(&alg, &sr);
449 dns_name_init(&tsig->algorithm, NULL);
450 RETERR(name_duporclone(&alg, mctx, &tsig->algorithm));
451
452 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&tsig->algorithm));
453
454 /*
455 * Time Signed.
456 */
457 INSIST(sr.length >= 6);
458 tsig->timesigned = ((uint64_t)sr.base[0] << 40) |
459 ((uint64_t)sr.base[1] << 32) |
460 ((uint64_t)sr.base[2] << 24) |
461 ((uint64_t)sr.base[3] << 16) |
462 ((uint64_t)sr.base[4] << 8) |
463 (uint64_t)sr.base[5];
464 isc_region_consume(&sr, 6);
465
466 /*
467 * Fudge.
468 */
469 tsig->fudge = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
470 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
471
472 /*
473 * Signature Size.
474 */
475 tsig->siglen = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
476 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
477
478 /*
479 * Signature.
480 */
481 INSIST(sr.length >= tsig->siglen);
482 tsig->signature = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, tsig->siglen);
483 if (tsig->signature == NULL)
484 goto cleanup;
485 isc_region_consume(&sr, tsig->siglen);
486
487 /*
488 * Original ID.
489 */
490 tsig->originalid = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
491 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
492
493 /*
494 * Error.
495 */
496 tsig->error = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
497 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
498
499 /*
500 * Other Size.
501 */
502 tsig->otherlen = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
503 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
504
505 /*
506 * Other.
507 */
508 INSIST(sr.length == tsig->otherlen);
509 tsig->other = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, tsig->otherlen);
510 if (tsig->other == NULL)
511 goto cleanup;
512
513 tsig->mctx = mctx;
514 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
515
516 cleanup:
517 if (mctx != NULL)
518 dns_name_free(&tsig->algorithm, tsig->mctx);
519 if (mctx != NULL && tsig->signature != NULL)
520 isc_mem_free(mctx, tsig->signature);
521 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
522}
523
524static inline void
525freestruct_any_tsig(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
526 dns_rdata_any_tsig_t *tsig = (dns_rdata_any_tsig_t *) source;
527
528 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
529 REQUIRE(tsig->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_tsig);
530 REQUIRE(tsig->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_any);
531
532 if (tsig->mctx == NULL)
533 return;
534
535 dns_name_free(&tsig->algorithm, tsig->mctx);
536 if (tsig->signature != NULL)
537 isc_mem_free(tsig->mctx, tsig->signature);
538 if (tsig->other != NULL)
539 isc_mem_free(tsig->mctx, tsig->other);
540 tsig->mctx = NULL;
541}
